# Build output only — regenerated by scripts/demo-build.sh.
# The page SNAPSHOTS (pages/, pages.json) are deliberately COMMITTED: they are the demo's data, and a
# deploy that has to re-fetch three live websites (and run headless Chromium for the reference renders)
# is a deploy that breaks when a site changes its markup or a runner has no network. Re-bake them on the
# audit cadence with scripts/demo-pages.sh, and commit the result — the demo then ages forward
# deliberately rather than drifting silently.
manuk_demo.js
manuk_demo_bg.wasm
